title: Riot
body: I don't even got my gold icon! Pls help me!!

replies.body:
There are some [current issues](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) with some players getting ranked rewards on EUNE. We're taking a look into this, so if you reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), we'll take a look into this further.

Let me know if you have any questions.
